@startuml chirgjin_track-my-events

participant "Frontend" as FE
participant "Gateway Service" as GW
participant "User Service" as US
participant "Tracking Service" as TS
participant "Redis" as RD
participant "PostgreSQL" as DB

FE -> GW: User registration request
GW -> US: Forward registration request
US -> DB: Create user record
DB --> US: Confirm user creation
US --> GW: Registration response
GW --> FE: Registration confirmation

FE -> GW: User login request
GW -> US: Forward login request
US -> DB: Verify credentials
DB --> US: Credentials verified
US --> GW: Login response with tokens
GW --> FE: Login confirmation and tokens

FE -> GW: Request API key
GW -> US: Forward API key request
US -> DB: Generate and store API key
DB --> US: API key generated
US --> GW: API key response
GW --> FE: API key

FE -> GW: Track event (via SDK)
GW -> RD: Publish event data
RD -> TS: Event data received
TS -> DB: Store event data
DB --> TS: Confirm data storage

FE -> GW: Request dashboard data
GW -> TS: Forward dashboard data request
TS -> DB: Fetch event statistics
DB --> TS: Event statistics
TS --> GW: Dashboard data response
GW --> FE: Dashboard data

@enduml